text: Paja de Sombrero is a corregimiento in Gualaca District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 653 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 670; its population as of 2000 was 637. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
